Package service

package service
  • Class
    Description
    ApplicantService
    Provides services specific to BTO Applicants, handling project viewing, applications, status checks, withdrawals, enquiries, and eligibility.
    HdbManagerService
    Provides services specific to HDB Managers, handling project management, officer assignment, and application approval.
    HdbOfficerService
    Provides services specific to HDB Officers, handling project viewing, application processing, and enquiry handling.
    IApplyableService
    Defines application-related operations for users who can apply for projects and submit enquiries.
    IAuthService
    Defines the contract for user authentication services.
    IEligibilityCheck
    Defines the contract for checking applicant eligibility for BTO projects/flats.
    IPasswordService
    Defines the contract for password management services.
    IProjectView
    Consolidated interface for project viewing capabilities across all user types.
    IReportService
    Defines the contract for generating reports based on BTO application and booking data.
    UserService
    Base class for user-related services, providing common authentication and password management functionalities.
